  "body": "Mainnet. Today's devel.\r\n\r\n- i removed all CL-related databases: tmp, nodes, beacon_indicies, etc...\r\n- started\r\n- caplin showing `Downloading History blk/sec=68.9 peers=14`\r\n- Grafana showing `ingress network traffic (mean for 30min): 120kb/s`. Looks small. I checked Google Cloud monitoring - it shows 8mb/s (and in grafana I see 8mb/s writes to disk). \r\n- Seems it's sentry's problem (or caplin's libp2p): it doesn't account p2p traffic to metrics `p2p_ingress`/`p2p_egress`",
